<A NAME="topicBasicFullscreen"></A>

<H2>Full screen</H2>
This function is useful if you want to see the visualization area in full screen.<P>

<H2>Usage</H2>

<OL>

<LI>
Press "Ctrl + F".

<LI>
The visualization area will occupy all the screen.

</OL>

<H2>Shortcuts</H2>

<UL>
<LI> Ctrl + F - Enable/disable full screen.
</UL>


